title: Is Something Wrong With Baltimore? Plus: The Underrated Bills, the Dangerous Dolphins, and More Week 9 Trends.
description:
We break down the Bills' unexpected blowout over the Seahawks and the Ravens' disappointing first half of the season (1:00), try to explain why the Chargers keep losing (18:00) and why the Dolphins should be taken seriously (28:00), discuss which NFC team you should trust the most, and preview (43:00) 'Thursday Night Football' (46:00).
Hosts: Chris Vernon and Warren Sharp
